The paper deals with image registration using deep learning methods, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of tissue clearing protocols and high-resolution imaging also suggests that the paper may fall under the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
